{"tid":1662564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援反送中被拒發行！謝和弦解約華納音樂「台灣快樂重要」","createTime":"2019-10-19T00:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T18:33:01.000Z","uid":33359,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9111ba3a46c01447bd9d885f7e838a8f266eadc2","tid":1662564,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:11:57.000Z","msg":"記者李嘉翎／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌手謝和弦向來有話直說，相當關心時事，不畏流言勇敢發聲，對於近日燒得沸沸揚揚的香港「反送中」事件，他也多次表達力挺，不過先前他透露自己寫了一首台灣歌，所屬華納音樂卻不敢發行，日前又在臉書公開私訊對話，痛批公司裝逼、不大器，今（18）日他宣布已與華納和平解約，高喊：「台灣快樂重要！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝和弦（圖／翻攝自IG） ID-2069322<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/08/12/2069322-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F2069322-XXL.jpg&h=9e5304d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲謝和弦屢次勇敢表達自己立場。（圖／翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝和弦2014年正式簽進華納音樂，並在去年續約，不過近日似乎頻頻與公司發生矛盾，日前他透露自己很久沒創作台語歌，寫了一首台灣的歌，但華納音樂卻因有所顧慮而不敢發行，他霸氣表示：「沒關係，我自己出錢製作，自己出錢拍MV！」甚至表示想回到陶山音樂。沒幾天又PO出一張詢問歌曲與詞曲版權授權事宜的私訊截圖，直言：「那我想離開華納了。」還在貼文寫下：「裝逼的國際公司，真不大器。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝和弦稱躁鬱症發後，時不時發生暴走狀況 。（圖／翻攝自謝和弦IG） ID-2167061<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲謝和弦和華納解約。（圖／翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日謝和弦在臉書曬出一張自拍照，寫下：「我老婆說我只要乖乖的聽話，靠這張臉其實可以賺很多錢。但我想聽自己心裡的話，那些年謝謝華納音樂，我們很和平的解約了，你覺得當偶像重要，還是台灣快樂重要。」宣布和合作5年的華納音樂解約。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝和弦/臉書 ID-2193373<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/18/2193373-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F18%2F2193373-XXL.jpg&h=a013acf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲謝和弦臉書PO文。（圖／翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉絲看了貼文後，一面倒力挺，除了感激華納當年不畏負評簽下謝和弦，讓更多人認識他外，也留言表示：「謝謝你愛台灣」、「堅持做對的事最帥氣」、「扣哥加油！需要支持台灣的音樂來支持愛台灣的精神！」、「因為謝和弦愛台灣，所以我支持你，感謝台灣有你！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/e/News.aspx?NewsID=620848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D620848&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9t%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=1a8e3de6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D620848&h=7d859b27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/e/News.aspx?NewsID=620848</a>"},{"pid":"856694f2fa88eeb2499610100952fc1a7e5f1236","tid":1662564,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:13:43.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"e003682b206bfffa7349b546bb410fd56239fb28","tid":1662564,"uid":30372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:14:00.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"b7da522333cfd96b838f7786504f8d131859319b","tid":1662564,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69685cd0cb39501fd4e04e1673f6cba1a8ebce9","tid":1662564,"uid":40439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"原來無咩台灣藝人表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3312f90d1c3dbbb3d61325649f655559f842d8","tid":1662564,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f69685cd0cb39501fd4e04e1673f6cba1a8ebce9","tid":1662564,"uid":40439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"原來無咩台灣藝人表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:17:56.000Z","msg":"雙十節夠膽出PO慶祝既都好少"},{"pid":"24d476c78ee58fca33fd47bed12df195a461924e","tid":1662564,"uid":103826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:21:10.000Z","msg":"r chord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d4d127c7fe5c4709d76ef8ac33b8399c0a9b11","tid":1662